data.description: Motivated Seller.....LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! This very well maintenance 4-bedroom 2.5 bath brick 2813 heating and cooled square foot home sits right in the heart of our hometown. The property is just steps from schools, churches, Crosby Commons, and situated on 3 city lots! This beautiful home offers a large kitchen, formal living and dining rooms, large sun drench family room, spacious bedrooms that all have their own access to a bath. The huge master bedroom opens up to the outside courtyard where you could enjoy your morning coffee. This is a must see. Call today for your showing,
